settings.title: Assembly Guide Video Walkthrough
settings.content: We prepared a video guide to help you with the installation process and to ensure it's safe and secure in the best condition.

If you already own an freebeat product, or if you just have pre-sales questions, the freebeat technical support team is available to help!

Each product has a dedicated support page on the website where you can find manuals, specifications, software updates, drivers and troubleshooting guides.

Connect with any of the following support options: online community support, live chat support or email support.
